      fix: 'The AIM Act phases down HFC PRODUCTION and IMPORT via a declining allowance system (85% cut by 2036). Separately, the Technology Transitions rule sets sector GWP limits (e.g., <700 for new residential AC). Reclaim/servicing continues even as new supply shrinks.',
