      fix: 'When a higher-efficiency or differently-fueled appliance is connected, the existing chimney/liner may be oversized (poor draft, condensation) or chemically incompatible with the new flue gases. Relining or a dedicated vent is often required — an existing chimney is not automatically reusable.',
